      "text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">During a regional conference on disaster management, a 40-year-old public health official emphasized the importance of consistent and sustained efforts to enhance a nation&#39;s resilience against various emergencies. He discusses investing in infrastructure, training, and resources not just for immediate response but for the holistic improvement of a nation&#39;s ability to manage any crisis. Which of the following terms best describes this approach?</span></span></p>",
